  <!-- FAQs Widget ******************* -->

  <FAQs
    title="Frequently Asked Questions"
    subtitle="Dive into the following questions to gain insights into what makes Oasis special."
    tagline="FAQs"
    classes={{ container: 'max-w-6xl' }}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Why would I not just use Slack?',
        description:
          "We aren't trying to compete with Slack for starters. But the simple answer to this is that our tool is build especially for GTM professionals and partnership teams to facilitate cross organizational collaboration, where Slack requires a restrictive Pro subscription to take advantage of cross-organizational collaboration to it's full extent. This can often cost tens of thousands of dollars at large organizations, where our base collaboration package will only require a monthly subscription of $350",
      },
      {
        title: 'Why is realtime collaboration important?',
        description:
          "We believe that the power of tools like Slack lies in the ability to send a message while it is top of mind, and get a reply at the earliest possible convenience. This is a missing piece in PRMs today.",
      },
      {
        title: 'How does this compare to tools like PartnerStack?',
        description:
