      },
      {
        title: 'What integrations do you support for account mapping?',
        description:
          "Right now, only Hubspot, but in the future we will be supporting Salesforce, Pipedrive, and more. If you have a specific tool you'd like us to support, please let us know.",
      },
      {
        title: "What's your pricing model?",
        description:
          "We offer two seperate pricing packages, one for our community features and one for our Sales plan. The community package is $350/mo and the Sales package is $2500/mo.",
      },
      {
        title: 'How do you handle security?',
        description:
          "We use WebAuthn to handle passwordless auth, but we also plan to support enterprise SSO in the near future. All of our data is encrypted at the application level and we use a variety of security tools to ensure that our application is secure. For our enterprise customers, we offer the ability to host Oasis on your own infrastructure, and are working on E2EE channels that should be available in the near future.",
      },
    ]}
